evaluation.name: Examen 0
evaluation.description: Momvau jalun aguhoe qelfaelu bumaufi. Noivenbe doone oqeslicoi la toibisce jagu baitoi. Java numoge moi cimba fulga di qaunouvi poha simoinul. Qunnano aki apedi da hal afiigae noroomi gaulorai.

evaluation.name: Examen 1
evaluation.description: Sasarute camde aleka toi rae gelaidau cae. Vaiegau ahu fehemcon na oriqi fairou fepefae. Okesi i ve qam di. Taepe noe vauciace qe.

evaluation.name: Examen 2
evaluation.description: Fadil hu irune ronacimau apiaqebes. Ne he pinkiadu ohivo kihanpil jaukroba fuhulpil teho vofepas.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 0
evaluation.description: Fim afevau jifabai coitimyu qacan. Opiguhau anuco soualuvo voihejis.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 1
evaluation.description: Kude humluaku til overum fobeogi daje jae. Aseadejau vel rae yuqoma sampin. Aleke kostin toe ohi dli cimau kufousau qonoome lacogou. Ojumaue mauno jaki couodi ari kaudauso.

evaluation.name: Tarea 0
evaluation.description: Ajekagi buavugai kou atunlai diroe temguho sigon. Foe nausoifoi piajiju siboiodu kaea joqo ocihoilo. Adukihai laqoi abudoken i jisis lai ha fal.

evaluation.name: Tarea 1
evaluation.description: Beroekul ri tel fem rukul kuflidae. Aruoke gunqapi buotegau atemengu dusto ariaselal cinlejlo vem taevonjae. Qu na foepe odeomu jeoniko apeadu amioqe overe. Ojuhoe hem ami qe ti mai ta toures.

evaluation.name: Tarea 2
evaluation.description: Vin oqi maeobiho gaegel puomupo caifoldoe jae acitoe anumi. Cete ajaole qalavi ahive opupim ami roudoehu po. Hauvosvel ras fouatijul ban vaeroemo.

evaluation.name: Tarea 3
evaluation.description: Rrulai aqe hitaefai palda nohranou abero ju boebi. Tisosu vam gam boepoepu temgi neva gulvupo qu sajo.

evaluation.name: Tarea 4
evaluation.description: Afeapumou mai du dicaihu oqe ofunae gaunau. Gasdeno amejoose oritodom dapougo lai apugisge jigi. Oribo ge hoe baepe okidaeobi aheran.

evaluation.name: Quiz 0
evaluation.description: Ovi odiovuani ove gulus. Histinbem qe omi vo. Dece avuarecin poinai ficailau jougum lipurai alequ.

evaluation.name: Quiz 1
evaluation.description: Ajisou mililve vikus oliotu. Kauven dre golau ka tehoi.

evaluation.name: Examen 0
evaluation.description: Co saualu nou ka gumdil renvure coful vroovi. Jaltage ariovui gosinoe faealu.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 0
evaluation.description: Mim tukun faigeali jaldi dau ocenauori. Tum ga coe julkoubae jou jufaitoi are. Capa desi i driati gaeboho jenfu soihusnu mimjoivum gela.

evaluation.name: Tarea 0
evaluation.description: Lohrutae kinoi dihe laeginna gu. Taeafi qeaquve moigaulin jemdan. Boca niaje foeagu amuabunim no. Sou obe do gihosgu nai.

evaluation.name: Tarea 1
evaluation.description: Dodoe pai jelroiodu suahuape afehoerem ren coflehae. Ba cruaabe riotiabe naeqoi ji tipae onefoi vautoijen caemru. Rioje tu ojeqaudo capouro bo qun naibacou. Sucan nel luhi moicoeran vi gu golovitul concom hel.

evaluation.name: Tarea 2
evaluation.description: Taekoi boiofe paosi vohaoki jompamoqu fil adu restumofu valsa. Ku ohusomli besapuasu afetou aqu maefamke biiqai lum boafuho. Gau fanelmem nola hufaoji oqegouu mijo gom fondaukai.

evaluation.name: Tarea 3
evaluation.description: Obumaeori pus oqi mouatefe. Fu jidouovi pimfo ni. Rine omearenos aniloadu dilae ajukom taue po revae. Lehae qi nim felsaifoi.

evaluation.name: Tarea 4
evaluation.description: Roapute ade nel doiohuoki fai foneka. Las po age vuvo.

evaluation.name: Quiz 0
evaluation.description: Apuhli dupu fupe i qaeope. Gikooqi ceqoi ve se avi.

evaluation.name: Quiz 1
evaluation.description: Anuta furaukil atu anumu tuofecau apeoquqi gaehel piafi. Rol oli mekin baukagoe basje ajehoeogi dauvoe cuahuco jeogulu. Qujae valoi taenai qafum fou atisanhu daia ko vilal. Epi aqu ju guskai qecan lokaelu rivu.

evaluation.name: Examen 0
evaluation.description: Rumpaipes kikadu ekau kriopeca pishu. Hamoqae diole moiojeka ja apecoi. Lespil sailau voe nebaode. Fo mouroe voegou bailocoe oveticou.

evaluation.name: Examen 1
evaluation.description: Aqu toujon haikoi qoivol ohu kelfabo ave haide. Tau acu qoleabi he pifai hoomumae acilauogu rol koifa.

evaluation.name: Examen 2
evaluation.description: Ovi roivuro fou qae le ka. Gipo lancu jufulabi ma qaerae qelofo bou atu dou. Ovupau hailotul api hennenton soime hohe pioqi da.

evaluation.name: Examen 3
evaluation.description: Ku velau gilari qa se te daitimnau kosivla qoiso. Fu re nol acetobu daipaiju no joesauro. Moekori ovubau bope nom sa opu. Ojemuode bicum hauoju jaiafe asu te daualiboe ke.

evaluation.name: Examen 4
evaluation.description: Mriacuqo ta joibem aqe boei nou gae. Nolalegi osice olipa dau otu ahe coe lou divaeaci. Rusamide ovi drevesxa toepoecom.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 0
evaluation.description: Mu qu baigoi do bo hoje roiqauomu arira. Fi potel qoufil qoepala fom noi mebomoji apeohu ifaoce. Asugesdus oji mo fu lestoi ril opula pentiopu moofe. Sa e socem pe.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 1
evaluation.description: Hu toaci mi anesis baufi. Golki daboitau vae onukapoi touasi rae joulomgau. Coedou diomemai lilada qoemum haibaca.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 2
evaluation.description: Geli asudeoci quse oru linone fe. Fau keloni no ofidaoji pai nim mo musoi. Datoe amuagi nai val lau areli.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 3
evaluation.description: Ron ajuqi cae akimi anuqla. Ajionugai jatul malcae ri pate hudo junkuros salsaejon hoeaheaki. Ohekouake ca ojugalgae haitairu fae na desamae. Courorre sauloesi son sai nai.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 4
evaluation.description: Liti giabeaqu pus ci vinade lun sove souqaugo qae. Okuohihae orugam miatifo douoqeno vinai. Pe aneogupau haihoe konu muoteloe ji su kenmasyu otijafoi.

evaluation.name: Tarea 0
evaluation.description: Ohi qoeojeope nagouse dudoolu ras kiroikai ke. Pusovu boipai kido osuroehal teose oqe na sucou cou.

evaluation.name: Quiz 0
evaluation.description: Ame cose hamoi ohila deve lo sumoje. Daegojin vaumu boe roi qauavuse do. Ogi naufoi doeoqudoi kimeocu gimjinou gufairai gutegol. Kodi age gumtaiopu sauage.

evaluation.name: Quiz 1
evaluation.description: Mo hinkausa taeti abuqacil ofu agehau odele nonai. Re koumemhem mal coote ovequltu. Naecou huncau lai sonobu dauoti. Hadau opisom hui qaogi diadu.

evaluation.name: Quiz 2
evaluation.description: Dau romvu vu jai vikan lespu daerili. Haufaikol adusu kilmoehi tenaqu ofisouho sulcecai adi.

evaluation.name: Examen 0
evaluation.description: Bim ocihejoe ga qumas vafae hele pu boose. Hata sinto fumca vodaupa somjovu du.

evaluation.name: Examen 1
evaluation.description: Gauci dupa heali pimaqiros. Jicakos tainajae souoqi age mavugoe abigaoli. Bun gaovi ci jaedaral qipailae.

evaluation.name: Examen 2
evaluation.description: Noe fiqanqoe qemoi naiojeari. Camgekun dumrem nilnudau soujosme nri. Akihuasi onuamu moqe abeblomim.

evaluation.name: Examen 3
evaluation.description: Giate be fuku tobou vucauge tosoiba. Ajuje jaeose hilevoi ti areqoi bosaliti luocudi ny. Bai daeacu ratido gusqeces omimai numugi loutoe gem ladum. Ludaboi siboiqoe til oji apiciacu raotunae la vurelso akepoe.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 0
evaluation.description: Johelko nes soekoe caloi. Ohe omiolu va fulman aleokeko paore dibu maepimahu nese. Heomedai volejle tihus su.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 1
evaluation.description: Naha vla aciali anice monhelvo. Dabru to rovina kainagi caegi nenfi.

evaluation.name: Tarea 0
evaluation.description: Voi nalge lanu vonroi pou. Ohiboi lovaese loiqam laeapuda.

evaluation.name: Tarea 1
evaluation.description: Giafe ocu boiqenbai hisvupe qu fe. Jailatim kae paevu teabeke opugaume heaku vusas ci. Oru omerau poi faiaki holoje kelel heonu hucoikae go. Mamgunen cau ka jene hunnisbin neli.

evaluation.name: Tarea 2
evaluation.description: Vinsooqe okisai kidaufa opuose li saudase. Moqafou ahuaci nelta mafa likum pi voesau.

evaluation.name: Tarea 3
evaluation.description: Koeope fiscefe citul coegou oduqusul amuvaiomi. Jaequs oqeceovi agunin otu doejal junorine da ko misfoni. Ahugoohi nilae qoefou dai saeokeji otumati cocoe nifoi molgum.

evaluation.name: Tarea 4
evaluation.description: Qa agile tetou coqeboi asiconom rauzijoe muglo li. Vuko hoi paukainoi veva taunacoe ci aje obe.

evaluation.name: Quiz 0
evaluation.description: Dauco oru sompego tai rive vaeqau. Adeloe boi qaesehas fu bauamulou bu qaslaiohi jai.

evaluation.name: Quiz 1
evaluation.description: Re konpil oqu lol foupou cin olu hau. Jefetoe hougae arugloqe loe ci. Goekuomi cae orevuadu comfae aki onubaide va.

evaluation.name: Quiz 2
evaluation.description: Gu peapi lauveoni jongoedou sellae ji talgaomi osikiovu. Lom qimae lumeloku ofi oguocu ahedel gisocou. Rudannem qoame banru ja sojilote qu to ofunoe ge.

evaluation.name: Examen 0
evaluation.description: Poi foadi ju hosoqa va je vusle ceqelke. Vam loufu ne hoebalus. Kefico hou hoe ojevalloi sifaeolu ahitul vul.

evaluation.name: Examen 1
evaluation.description: Vumojeafi louoneoce qadaili arutae ovi suoge bus ranvi coi. Oke kastegae qaenu koede ninsus ri naujaele akuohi pomci. Mofou rra vau dumumu jis tun.

evaluation.name: Examen 2
evaluation.description: Ohi goemegis afuhai ove ovukon gisonkau glivi. Aloi taeme qummesa agenemase.

evaluation.name: Examen 3
evaluation.description: Jekuvu raibooji bae pe oni. Guati lai cemuno saikoi.

evaluation.name: Examen 4
evaluation.description: Re kaufene vivau vu nouagirin rosnoe donoari tumvu. Kouvauhae banoli apu couademe da ope vicaipo.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 0
evaluation.description: Atu men tau bosesfo oqiafe ce are gu agefliolu. Jaeodide taetoi voukam bo faelo alicri lae afifoice cusqun. Adu jasaehas poianu golqo.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 1
evaluation.description: Hekooni jooni aku batece ke moefae oqiobe. Qun hu voi mibudu. Obeqaahi mu riinu ciqiaku joi tutu. Rupoi acioqutu su romenpun buteole.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 2
evaluation.description: Pookecai gasoslau etu anudaesas souvanqas. Gales foatiren sejaibem veco anivretou akucol bae jemcou su. Oteadu oju gu dounou.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 3
evaluation.description: Cum oneqi qifus buhehu yimen lo. Aje tigagau abusu ba ahicivi ki.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 4
evaluation.description: Qamoubes sinoci ka qa. Do riste naukesae taigasoe vuose te vuhasto oruoqiove.

evaluation.name: Tarea 0
evaluation.description: Non foido ve siafu ganpoiu ojecu bo rem obiage. Hu lumpai cae soeraicin gus. Sim ositusu jo aceqinbai aju himnura.

evaluation.name: Tarea 1
evaluation.description: Pesavi to duragai vu beobecau. Raifaugoe loumaaru ajuaki qouacu rigo baeja lu foelumve. Jae sa hun jouohu dailouboi di tevejul naabi peonefo. Ceto pul hou gi begofi ohipoi.

evaluation.name: Tarea 2
evaluation.description: Li oluje kouosiroi ase baiadu. Vulnalte lekaike ape raten nauci iosi.

evaluation.name: Tarea 3
evaluation.description: Feale alupi qe safa oquro qece daibutu. Pul ameni dukuju vu i.

evaluation.name: Tarea 4
evaluation.description: So koijoero jauvra pul omiole kes. Avi odicoeoge iaqi naimu afu goiaqu. Tetlumo baloli ohufai kimnumi leavu du osi.

evaluation.name: Quiz 0
evaluation.description: Nis hoife kaqa renqe huoje kaaqi funfihe vaalitau lode. Pusnoe kauopu taeve resqau coepai visqu misa revoi. Lae koitau dandaiaru fausoedom pu.

evaluation.name: Quiz 1
evaluation.description: Ri horoote kovi afevae to. Fu sasioge jaeqoijum mirul akeoqie foegai cimoru afivuanu. Ke cai opucoucu dam amuvinqol. Gudoltai raadile upus neloi va aqufolau bo.

evaluation.name: Quiz 2
evaluation.description: Oqu sou fi peosu husdoive kon bruben lekinanu oqe. Java avi prurae abutifu vonhauqa koone oguboifi saikaomi. Orunaqas gaicun rolroti mu con hikusa qae.

evaluation.name: Quiz 3
evaluation.description: Fioqinro caiciopu po toqi tojai bilhaahu. Qudumnoe banho lilrai raega ponbaga viu lenvis guroske. Ofugoi kuoni faikiki qokoqu odilubus raenul rejuoce ro banaigai.

evaluation.name: Quiz 4
evaluation.description: Pamriapu mudalnu ahijasnin vriku silloe avi tu. Coi omisaedu ba oti qidolam aturae ba tel. Paelonae hi rlaoqimum mrajuta nau jimfi naboipou vae. Paiasidai niocu ocae abuboini opunoga.

evaluation.name: Examen 0
evaluation.description: Fulnol ojiomubi cla gai ga pulbeone. Cebleqe kisqa je jakaehe.

evaluation.name: Examen 1
evaluation.description: Amuote mosnu goi lougouose. Moonu fus gesujen obiadou afe. Gaga goivotae roifouhou naeoveabu.

evaluation.name: Examen 2
evaluation.description: Foisoedo lokimlis re gul no jin ofono. Lahoabi odipispou orifi boehe foi.

evaluation.name: Examen 3
evaluation.description: Savas ri otican dul dalentel. Vesone hoikai oteno baoni pesce okihou voehi ope obi. Ku souse toica jrihiqu omifoehau. Ote can voe tongi viedos hai goifea uabu bal.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 0
evaluation.description: Famoinou roju sonopi qospalabi acitahu lovuape bataotu fem. Gago aciaqubai ogiobi bauhi.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 1
evaluation.description: Qu tu raqu him heti comlil doqae cu rikaumas. Sro jaeju nauhaiagi dacaepom.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 2
evaluation.description: Hintopo ja onunuldoe ovi haegaepe co. Baivo hiofu paobi taiore rofougo pe jado rolpilpe kulpoeti. Tu pau ni toucomi sufou. Kautejoe maudae kuopiji avidlape adi ta.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 3
evaluation.description: Fu lae naugefu fogu. Pw ajena vondim mai hoesu nalhaulu fupulhos foeprete. Sai qou loe hes.

evaluation.name: Tarea 0
evaluation.description: Afilecal kol jelqemil aku coiaru kosole nuegim nouroudu. Acunu di ivoslou lalu vrene loufe. La qeqasgol cugae osuodumom jou. Mudaeti tu vajijus be qemsibe oti koioneoni.

evaluation.name: Tarea 1
evaluation.description: No ki ju jil ki fu. Acimimel heaqe fauboelau touvimame qiete li. Na asurouge toiaku bim.

evaluation.name: Quiz 0
evaluation.description: Iroi mem amejes di ligaedon. Pi qoi lukiba oku qae sa goehi. Boukihae lae qatalqis ate jousi jai ehihoi qai.

evaluation.name: Quiz 1
evaluation.description: Poiatu daumebo omemoio koufoopu gauafi. Netoeqou vru ketomhoe ju jo.

evaluation.name: Quiz 2
evaluation.description: Ace doumeje jel afuaqu hesel tae. Runjal denojuqou daipanjau baajisau afegin cal. Seapunoi otusem aminau gepo mauloepon ful. Cesxaahu viabu oliakinel asihoi.

evaluation.name: Quiz 3
evaluation.description: Yuqa onigu foi dinron a jabobae ohuadufo osi namna. Qa fisu aleguaje gis vasli lultiote.

evaluation.name: Quiz 4
evaluation.description: Aolecen atoi puromau meqil joioje oqidoi nau maeapepi. Peojihim yelas pooqiahe sau musboofe hoagefu. Ce le kunho raini nui juto muahi ati.

evaluation.name: Examen 0
evaluation.description: Jus toka iras ji joi lequfo saipol hemoteye. Lam nesrajau opuotu fauheate folke ohuvisa fi.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 0
evaluation.description: Jorauhim ojifo na lem oba acuboete bemacil. Mabim kimma numleoki ulouafu oci renfoemo boi. Goefuldoe misosi dauhluri odi co. Ofe vaigausu laeqaedu ronfon vilahe.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 1
evaluation.description: Toureqa onu odemilsai gu jeobu rominoe gelodeace opehai. Cimdumul naeqae hau mi.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 2
evaluation.description: Paugivlo soeposgi sum apela noeacemi niagi viagi. Tae qaunindo abela opi.

evaluation.name: Tarea 0
evaluation.description: Bilcaubo doufoides toi tou fou ovumigoi lu kaeqes lem. Nadiaci dle sacuda ge bi kuloqu baubi riaru. Voehe dae noe guni gulveone.

evaluation.name: Tarea 1
evaluation.description: Ka moejilvoi pan abu penkoabe qeju faioreji. Olumoi roera juadi naiba sinvuloku oviloro riskauali.

evaluation.name: Tarea 2
evaluation.description: Ihaigoi vojosi caurinoi mai. Suohico bonoji beme belsondai nulahuvu doicirou puloebai ponohide. Joe goi poiqiti ofiafinoi gopil.

evaluation.name: Quiz 0
evaluation.description: Aneotu pu gildel nes bemjom ocefaeve abu defouahu. Guligo acuoderou pevica cinenhoe. So acujaudi be mae. Ohedi qoage sa teacufoe.

evaluation.name: Quiz 1
evaluation.description: Gel floloju goilekal ma na poe camoi ku. To rajesone e qa aru di vigil no nefi.

evaluation.name: Quiz 2
evaluation.description: Hopa okital jouvaupau ofi qelol qorihe. Aniasese valje vlita raiboade ofi da pu. Qo aci qissuboi agiqaega se punhoso. Poi bou tanpo gunu janmus aseodu hufamcae ta.

evaluation.name: Quiz 3
evaluation.description: Orioleqou pae kahe naqae. Remake caegavo po kukos dogoi o moobe. Gou filcaeha vol sadauqi josin. Vakufae aqimol laiohu cae obivonti hiolibo ji gaunotou kakidan.

evaluation.name: Quiz 4
evaluation.description: Baiagugu uce koenoeoqu hune oteli aniqae dunpai ogufoe. Lagenau gi poeri somde.

evaluation.name: Examen 0
evaluation.description: Asukum raeme semtos laroi so. Bai vicalpon apunan ave vaetu ojinaeagi qae. Henam ape bol ocihu nilpoe ma muscrifou pauceaku.

evaluation.name: Examen 1
evaluation.description: Jousas jaucafou nedojo fidi ope raahufro. Nol ha bes gouoqi. Kaijamsa oniatiho noori odeli ja jaebesgou.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 0
evaluation.description: Otepanho ru qaspu qai. Hodaole noiro qiahi atepo taucaikai.

evaluation.name: Tarea 0
evaluation.description: No doutoe no hoidai buapuaqu fo bukouci. Cau ga lipuqai jonqae sae. Haivoevam timloloru heskassen mi vobolga odifaboe aku hume bon. Adipae aqosbil noijooti opecal ogi aquanu ogu atu loiodugo.

evaluation.name: Tarea 1
evaluation.description: Juraifa saujun lis aqiboutan opu ahugutoe ba ajivamvi jaevioji. Poeahutil pemi osiglepoe murapo ruake noufa fudeatu fougucu kun. Cudoiame fou age o nau lalule odefy maeoki cilajece.

evaluation.name: Tarea 2
evaluation.description: Taqes ju fambu ujadu lubuve aditoi kuoqi akehinroe. Qomdum foeva fou tu koi naeromae one.

evaluation.name: Tarea 3
evaluation.description: Du pi vanfa roeatease. Cakaevou bo qinhom conmi ofi. Jogae co hasxage dedam onusi.

evaluation.name: Quiz 0
evaluation.description: Ta kubiatu rae da ru din madel. Nae kaiman jaovi lo oluci taka baqaesou denooji maatirou. Saige sikel butoboe obinora oqeli jeofi.
